  <title>Providing Culturally and Linguistically Competent Care</title>
  <metadata xmlns:md="http://cnx.rice.edu/mdml">
    <md:title>Providing Culturally and Linguistically Competent Care</md:title>
    <md:content-id>m00019</md:content-id>
    <md:abstract><para id="para-00002">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
    <list id="list-00001">
      <item>Apply principles of culturally responsive care to populations and clients from diverse cultures.</item>
      <item>Create a plan of care with culturally specific interventions.</item>
      <item>Develop strategies to communicate with deaf populations or clients.</item>
      <item>Identify strategies to utilize when communicating through an interpreter.</item>
      <item>Evaluate translated materials for accuracy and effectiveness.</item>
    </list>
    </md:abstract>
